  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n\r\nNon-Latin nicknames in mentions are sent as plain text, so you can't navigate to the user's profile by clicking on it, and the recipient isn't notified that they've been mentioned.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nNicknames of any alphabets resolve in mentions\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/228322496-2570fd47-9c1e-48fc-a88d-caa351d87eda.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1. Open chat\r\n2. Add a non-Latin nickname to some user\r\n3. Try to mention them\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly 28/03\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
